Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:26.55,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}身陷于此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:33.53,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将再也见不到未来光芒
